Hospital.Argument

Interface PublicArgument<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the argument to be answered
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicArgument, BooleanArgument, CampusInfoArgument, IntegerArgument, ItemArgument, ListArgument, NoneArgument, PriorityArgument, StringArgument, TimeArgument, WorldArgument

    @SystemAPI
public interface PublicArgument<T>
    This class holds the answer to some information that is needed. A question is given for information purposes.
